# compact-guard.tape — vhs script for the compact-guard demo GIF.

Output "demos/compact-guard.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1080
Set Height 900
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-compact-guard.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 17s
